name: Oliver Janata
coverLetter: Been trimming for two years, can finish a pound in under 4 hours. I will be gone the 18th and 19th and then again from the 25th to the 30th. Other than that my sched is open. I can pitch a tent and stay on site or commute but i cant go more than 20 min out of grants pass if im commuting daily. I also have a years worth landscaping and construction experience.
